{
  "id": "5aPP91mj",
  "slug": "nmtp",
  "title": "No More Tree Punching",
  "description": "Makes the start of the Minecraft more challenging by adding new items and changing block drops.",
  "body": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/hXVChyJ/nmtp-title.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"949\" height=\"95\" /></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/fabric-api\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ol1Tcf8.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"205\" height=\"68\" /></a></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong>This mod is still under development, it will probably have a lot of bugs and errors. It also lacks some important features.&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\">This mod adds new items and changes the block drops to make the start of the game more challenging.&nbsp;</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\">In basic, this project is very similar to the <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/no-tree-punching\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">No Tree Punching</a> mod.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><font size=5><strong>TUTORIAL</strong></span></font></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">To break down log and wood blocks, you will now need an axe, but since you don't have access to the wood you can't craft a Wooden Axe, therefore will need to craft a Flint Axe.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">T</span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">o craft a Flint Axe you will need to craft a Flint Knife, which you can craft with 1 Stick and 1 Flint. With your Flint Knife, you can break grass and get Plant Fiber.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">After you get 3 Plant Fibers you can combine them and craft a Plant String.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">With 1 Stick, 1 Plant String, and 1 Flint you can finally craft a Flint Axe and break down wood.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><font size=5><strong>FEATURES</strong></span></p>\n<p></font>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<strong><font size=4>ITEMS</strong></span></font></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/47BScSX/plant-fiber.png\" width=\"39\" height=\"39\" /></strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\"><strong>Plant Fiber</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Can be gathered by breaking grass with knives.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">With 3 Plant Fiber, a <strong>Plant String</strong> can be crafted.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/CHZhJ5m/plant-string.png\" width=\"39\" height=\"39\" /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\"><strong>Plant String</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Needed to craft Flint Tools.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 18px;\">Those items below are also blocks, you can place them into the surface of other blocks. They don't spawn naturally like in the No Tree Punching mod though.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/NTT7SM6/loose-stone.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"39\" height=\"39\" /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 19px;\"><strong>Stone Rock</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">When a Stone is mined with the right tool, 4 Stone Rock will drop.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">4 of them can be crafted into a Cobblestone.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/6Y4DG91/loose-andesite.png\" width=\"39\" height=\"39\" /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Andesite Rock</strong></span></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">When a Andesite is mined with the right tool, 4 Andesite Rock will drop.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">4 of them can be crafted into a Andesite.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/NsJsbXs/loose-diorite.png\" width=\"39\" height=\"39\" /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Diorite Rock</strong></span></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">When a Diorite is mined with the right tool, 4 Andesite Rock will drop.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">4 of them can be crafted into a Diorite.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/XkKM4Qm/loose-granite.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"39\" height=\"39\" /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Granite Rock</strong></span></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">When a Diorite is mined with the right tool, 4 Andesite Rock will drop.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">4 of them can be crafted into a Diorite.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/NYdRHdD/loose-deepslate.png\" width=\"39\" height=\"39\" /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Deepslate Rock</strong></span></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">When a Diorite is mined with the right tool, 4 Andesite Rock will drop.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">4 of them can be crafted into a Diorite.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/4VK3jM9/loose-sandstone.png\" width=\"39\" height=\"39\" /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Sandstone Rock</strong></span></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">When a Diorite is mined with the right tool, 4 Andesite Rock will drop.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">4 of them can be crafted into a Diorite.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/tcYtt9z/loose-red-sandstone.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"39\" height=\"39\" /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Red Sandstone Rock</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">When a Diorite is mined with the right tool, 4 Andesite Rock will drop.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">4 of them can be crafted into a Diorite.</span>&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 21px; color: #ff6600;\"><strong><font size=5>TOOLS</strong></span></font></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/tQpdj2N/flint-sword.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"45\" height=\"45\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Flint Sword</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Damage: 3</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Attack Speed: 1.6</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/QN8PLrD/flint-axe.png\" width=\"45\" height=\"45\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Flint Axe</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Damage: 6</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Attack Speed: 0.7</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/nQWHCR7/flint-pickaxe.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"45\" height=\"45\" /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Flint Pickaxe</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Damage: 1</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Attack Speed: 1.2</span></p>\n<p><br /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/ZdFY6FS/flint-shovel.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"45\" height=\"45\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Flint Shovel&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Damage: 1.5</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Attack Speed: 1</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/NZ5k4c5/flint-hoe.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"45\" height=\"45\" /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Flint Hoe</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Damage: 1</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Attack Speed: 1</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/RSfsygk/flint-knife.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Flint Knife</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Damage: 1</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Attack Speed: 1.7</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/rQTxY83/wooden-knife.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" />\n\n<strong>Wooden Knife</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><b>Damage: 2</b></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><b>Attack Speed: 1.7</b></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><b><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/89BVtNs/gold-knife.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" /></b></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><b>Golden Knife</b></strong></span></p>\n<p><b><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Damage: 2</span></b></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><b>Attack Speed: 1.8</b></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><b><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/vhCs5FY/stone-knife.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" />\n\n<strong>Stone Knife</strong></b></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><b>Damage: 3</b></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><b>Attack Speed: 1.7</b></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><b style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/bHQMp7v/iron-knife.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" /></b></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><b><strong>Iron Knife</strong></b></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><b>Damage: 4</b></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><b>Attack Speed: 1.7</b></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><b><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/c1YzGt5/diamond-knife.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" /> \n\n<strong>Diamond Knife</strong></b></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><b>Damage: 5</b></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><b>Attack Speed: 1.7</b></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><b><br /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/WxcRGPT/netherite-knife.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" \n/>\n\nNetherite Knife</b></strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><b>Damage: 6</b></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><b>Attack Speed: 1.7</b></span></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><font size=5><strong>FAQ</strong></span></font></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 18px;\">Will you port this mod to Forge</strong>?</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">There is already a similar and even better mod for Forge called <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/no-tree-punching\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">No Tree Punching</a>, I recommend you use that. So the answer is no.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 18px;\">Can I use this mod on&nbsp;X</strong>?</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">You can use this mod freely in every project you want. But it would be nice if you credit me and the Alcatraz Escapee.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 18px;\">I found a bug / I have a suggestion, what should I do?</span></strong></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">You can comment or open an issue on <a href=\"https://github.com/spacegoat3/NoMoreTreePunching\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">GitHub</a><span style=\"color: #000000;\">.</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 18px;\">Will you port this mod to&nbsp;&lt;1.17</strong>?</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-size: 18px;\">I am sorry but no.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 22px; color: #ff0000;\">\n<p>&nbsp;</p><strong>DISCLAIMER / CREDITS</strong></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">This project is not connected to <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/no-tree-punching\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>No Tree Punching</strong></a> or <a href=\"http://www.alcatrazescapee.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Alcatraz Escapee</strong></a>.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">The original idea and most of the textures in the mod by <a href=\"http://www.alcatrazescapee.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Alcatraz Escapee</strong></a>.</span></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Have fun :D</strong></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
